                                                                  Height="100"
                                                                  VerticalContentAlignment="Top"
                                                                  IsReadOnly="True"
                                                                  Text="Order submission style for new auto-perms.&#10;Sequential: waits for the previous perm to cancel, or if it fills, waits for the resulting position to close before submitting the next perm.&#10;Slam: submits all perms simultaneously as soon as they are generated."
